{
  "texts": [
    "The artificial synapse array was synthesized using Cu/GeTe, while the artificial neuron was synthesized utilizing MoS 2.",
    "By programming the weights based on offline training mapping, the resulting synapse-neuron device array exhibited the desired integration-and-fire behavior.",
    "This experimental work serves as a significant demonstration of the potential for integrating synapses and neurons to realize functional behavior in neuromorphic systems.",
    "In-memory Circuit DesignIn addition to standalone crossbar arrays of memristors/ memtransistors, the integration of memristive devices with other circuit elements, such as capacitors and diodes, offers significant potential for achieving specialized functionalities.",
    "For instance, Dodda et al."
  ]
}